Portucel gains on pulp price optimism . Shares in pulp producer Portucel Industrial gained 1 . 8 percent to 1 , 099 escudos after a leading Swedish forestry group announced it might raise prices from mid - April , dealers said . Sodra did not say by how much and it was not possible to get an immediate reaction from Portucel on its own price plans . Portucel ' s stock was off early highs of 1 , 110 and was struggling to hold above 1 , 100 . " Maybe this time ( pulp ) prices will rise . But in the past there have been expectations for prices rises and then nothing happened , " said one trader . ( $ 1 = 168 . 39 escudos ) - - Lisboa Editorial , 351 - 1 - 3113125 . 
